explanation:
## Why Asked
Tests understanding of advanced architectural patterns for building scalable, fault-tolerant distributed systems.

## Key Concepts
- Immutable event log
- Command vs Event separation
- Snapshot optimization
- Event replay
- CQRS pattern
- Eventual consistency

## Code Example
```typescript
// Event structure
interface Event {
  id: string;
  type: string;
  aggregateId: string;
  timestamp: Date;
  data: any;
}

// Event store
class EventStore {
  private events: Event[] = [];

  save(event: Event) {
    this.events.push(event);
  }

  getEvents(aggregateId: string): Event[] {
    return this.events.filter(e => e.aggregateId === aggregateId);
  }
}
```

## Follow-up Questions
- How do you handle event versioning?
